    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting an incredible opportunity for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or swirl marks, and the interior remains in showroom state, retaining its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with zero regard for cost. It drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered, offering a rare chance to own a pristine example of this model.",
